From 6aab1f9391f9067f96c960c74bc1bd53dd05688f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Shankar Easwaran <seaswara@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 15:52:08 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] [AArch64] Static TLS support

Re-implement static TLS support for correctly handling TCB size
with varying alignments.

Symbol values during relocation only can be accessed by calling
getSymValue as per design.

The patch was trying to setup the GOT slots with values before the
values were finalized.

Signed-off-by: Shankar Easwaran <seaswara@qti.qualcomm.com>
(cherry picked from commit c3a38e17e34689471f195887e482ca48dec92f1c)
